cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper discusses optimization processes for solving large-scale problems and overcoming machine learning limitations, which are common topics in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). The focus on feature extraction and Meta-Learning algorithms further supports these sub-categories.
